<section aria-labelledby="faq-heading" class="section faq" id="faq">
<div class="container faq__inner">
<div class="section-header">
<span class="section-tag">Common Questions</span>
<h2 class="section-title" id="faq-heading">Questions We Hear From Local Business Owners</h2>
</div>
<div class="faq__list" role="list">
<div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
<button aria-controls="faq-a-1" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-item__question" id="faq-q-1">
              How long does it take to see SEO results?
              <span aria-hidden="true" class="faq-icon">+</span>
</button>
<div aria-labelledby="faq-q-1" class="faq-item__answer" hidden="" id="faq-a-1" role="region">
<p>Most clients see measurable improvements in rankings within 60–90 days. For highly competitive markets, it can take 4–6 months to reach the top positions. We set clear timelines based on your specific market and competition level during your free audit.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
<button aria-controls="faq-a-2" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-item__question" id="faq-q-2">
              Do I need to sign a long-term contract?
              <span aria-hidden="true" class="faq-icon">+</span>
</button>
<div aria-labelledby="faq-q-2" class="faq-item__answer" hidden="" id="faq-a-2" role="region">
<p>No. All of our plans are month-to-month. We don't believe in locking clients in — we believe in earning your business every month with real results. You can cancel at any time with 30 days' notice.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
<button aria-controls="faq-a-3" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-item__question" id="faq-q-3">
              What is AI-SEO and why does my business need it?
              <span aria-hidden="true" class="faq-icon">+</span>
</button>
<div aria-labelledby="faq-q-3" class="faq-item__answer" hidden="" id="faq-a-3" role="region">
<p>AI-SEO (also called GEO — Generative Engine Optimization) is the practice of optimizing your online presence so that AI-powered search tools like Google's AI Overviews, ChatGPT, and Perplexity recommend your business by name. As more people use AI to find local services, this is becoming as important as traditional SEO.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
<button aria-controls="faq-a-4" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-item__question" id="faq-q-4">
              Do you work with businesses in all industries?
              <span aria-hidden="true" class="faq-icon">+</span>
</button>
<div aria-labelledby="faq-q-4" class="faq-item__answer" hidden="" id="faq-a-4" role="region">
<p>Yes — we work with local businesses across all service industries including plumbing, HVAC, auto repair, restaurants, salons, dental practices, legal offices, retail shops, landscaping, roofing, and many more. If you serve local customers, we can help you get found.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
<button aria-controls="faq-a-5" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-item__question" id="faq-q-5">
              What does the free SEO audit include?
              <span aria-hidden="true" class="faq-icon">+</span>
</button>
<div aria-labelledby="faq-q-5" class="faq-item__answer" hidden="" id="faq-a-5" role="region">
<p>Your free audit covers: current keyword rankings, Google Business Profile health, website technical issues, competitor analysis, local citation gaps, review profile assessment, and a prioritized list of quick wins. You get this delivered in a clear, actionable PDF — no sales pitch required to receive it.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
<button aria-controls="faq-a-6" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-item__question" id="faq-q-6">
              Can you guarantee #1 rankings on Google?
              <span aria-hidden="true" class="faq-icon">+</span>
</button>
<div aria-labelledby="faq-q-6" class="faq-item__answer" hidden="" id="faq-a-6" role="region">
<p>No ethical SEO company can guarantee specific rankings — Google's algorithm is complex and constantly evolving. What we do guarantee is our process: proven strategies, transparent reporting, measurable month-over-month growth, and accountability. Our track record speaks for itself: 89% of clients reach page 1 within 90 days.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<script>
  const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.faq-item');

  faqItems.forEach((item) => {
    const button = item.querySelector<HTMLButtonElement>('.faq-item__question');
    const answer = item.querySelector<HTMLElement>('.faq-item__answer');
    if (!button || !answer) return;

    button.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const wasExpanded = button.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';

      faqItems.forEach((otherItem) => {
        const otherButton = otherItem.querySelector<HTMLButtonElement>('.faq-item__question');
        const otherAnswer = otherItem.querySelector<HTMLElement>('.faq-item__answer');
        if (otherButton !== button) {
          otherButton?.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
          otherAnswer?.setAttribute('hidden', '');
        }
      });

      button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(!wasExpanded));
      answer.toggleAttribute('hidden', wasExpanded);
    });
  });
</script>
